s and a single receiver or fully wireless\nagent, we show that $CR \\in [3,5.681319]$. Any group consisting of only senders\nor only receivers requires competitive ratio 9, and any other combination of\nagents has competitive ratio 3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Sep 2021 18:37:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-28"}
