ites and their few\nneighbors. Requiring only current level of technology, our scheme can be\nreadily tested in experiment and may pave an alternative way towards the future\ninvestigation of HOTIs in the presence of magnetic field, disorder, and strong\ncorrelation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Sep 2021 10:05:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-28"}
