a computational\npoint of view the proposed method is practical and can be implemented in a\nsimple and efficient way.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Sep 2021 15:54:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2022 08:40:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 24 Nov 2022 11:10:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-28"}
